{
  "stem": "12150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they had a secret service, spying on Jewish people, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So life changed completely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some people lost their livelihood within two years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took a business away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember all the details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family-- I-- as far as I remember, we also, in 1940 or '41, we also got a non-Jewish partner, who shared in everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Without investment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a prelude to confiscate the whole business, I figure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a contractor that my father did business with, years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now he became a partner, all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- they were assigned by the government, or the local government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- these details I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember it was bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, anyway, as far as I remember, we had enough food, at least, through the end-- as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one year, in 19-- well, I don't remember if I disclosed-- I must have disclosed to my father that I don't see any future staying in Munkats.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I suggested-- and besides, that was in 1940, already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We already heard what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had an uncle who was a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This must have been 1939 or 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they rounded up all Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were Polish citizens, living in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they transferred-- they transferred them to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I never heard of him since.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was a group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took them to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we never, never heard of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a year after that-- and I probably disclosed to my father, there's no future waiting here for the Germans to come in, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even under the Hungarians, there's no life here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's just fear, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
